      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are privileged to offer this impeccably preserved specimen, presented in showroom condition. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, exhibiting no signs of wear and retaining its original factory integrity. A superlative choice for the discerning collector or enthusiast, this motorcar represents a rare opportunity to acquire a turn-key asset of the highest caliber. We invite serious inquiries to experience the pristine nature of this exceptional vehicle firsthand.",
